**Greedy — fix captain by ratio**: Define ratio_i = wage[i] / quality[i]. The wage paid to anyone in the group is `groupRate * quality_i`, where `groupRate = max ratio` in the group. The total is `groupRate * sum(quality in group)`. We want to minimize this product.

